    "body": "\r\n### GPT-OSS-20B\r\n\r\n- SGLANG_USE_FLASHINFER_MXFP4_BF16_MOE=1\r\n\r\n```markdown\r\nCUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=1 SGLANG_USE_FLASHINFER_MXFP4_BF16_MOE=1 python3 -m sglang.launch_server --model-path openai/gpt-oss-20b --tp-size 1 --port 30001\r\n\r\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:30001/flush_cache\r\npython3 -m sglang.bench_serving --backend sglang-oai  --dataset-name random --random-input-len 512 --random-output-len 1024 --random-range-ratio 1 --num-prompts 20 --max-concurrency 1 --output-file res.jsonl --port 30001 --warmup-requests 10\r\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:30001/flush_cache\r\npython3 -m sglang.bench_serving --backend sglang-oai  --dataset-name random --random-input-len 512 --random-output-len 1024 --random-range-ratio 1 --num-prompts 200 --max-concurrency 32 --output-file res.jsonl --port 30001 --warmup-requests 10\r\n\r\n+----+-------------------+--------------------+---------------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------+\r\n|    |   max_concurrency |   input_throughput |   output_throughput |   mean_ttft_ms |   median_ttft_ms |   p99_ttft_ms |   mean_tpot_ms |   median_tpot_ms |   p99_tpot_ms |   per_user_throughput |\r\n+====+===================+====================+=====================+================+==================+===============+================+==================+===============+=======================+\r\n|  0 |             1.000 |            114.520 |             229.040 |         72.553 |           55.199 |       194.158 |          4.298 |            3.946 |         6.897 |               229.040 |\r\n+----+-------------------+--------------------+---------------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------+\r\n|  1 |            32.000 |           2301.694 |            4603.388 |        304.275 |          245.623 |       760.550 |          6.043 |            6.123 |         6.377 |               143.856 |\r\n+----+-------------------+--------------------+---------------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------+\r\n```\r\n\r\n- SGLANG_USE_FLASHINFER_MXFP4_MOE=1\r\n\r\n```markdown\r\nCUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=1 SGLANG_USE_FLASHINFER_MXFP4_MOE=1 python3 -m sglang.launch_server --model-path openai/gpt-oss-20b --tp-size 1 --port 30001\r\n\r\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:30001/flush_cache\r\npython3 -m sglang.bench_serving --backend sglang-oai  --dataset-name random --random-input-len 512 --random-output-len 1024 --random-range-ratio 1 --num-prompts 20 --max-concurrency 1 --output-file res.jsonl --port 30001 --warmup-requests 10\r\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:30001/flush_cache\r\npython3 -m sglang.bench_serving --backend sglang-oai  --dataset-name random --random-input-len 512 --random-output-len 1024 --random-range-ratio 1 --num-prompts 200 --max-concurrency 32 --output-file res.jsonl --port 30001 --warmup-requests 10\r\n\r\n+----+-------------------+--------------------+---------------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------+\r\n|    |   max_concurrency |   input_throughput |   output_throughput |   mean_ttft_ms |   median_ttft_ms |   p99_ttft_ms |   mean_tpot_ms |   median_tpot_ms |   p99_tpot_ms |   per_user_throughput |\r\n+====+===================+====================+=====================+================+==================+===============+================+==================+===============+=======================+\r\n|  0 |             1.000 |            184.744 |             369.488 |         40.923 |           43.838 |        54.155 |          2.668 |            2.667 |         2.685 |               369.488 |\r\n+----+-------------------+--------------------+---------------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------+\r\n|  1 |            32.000 |           2853.735 |            5707.471 |        257.555 |          240.758 |       512.740 |          4.859 |            4.862 |         5.046 |               178.358 |\r\n+----+-------------------+--------------------+---------------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------+\r\n```\r\n\r\n- PR\r\n\r\n```markdown\r\nCUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=1 python3 -m sglang.launch_server --model-path openai/gpt-oss-20b --tp-size 1 --port 30001\r\n\r\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:30001/flush_cache\r\npython3 -m sglang.bench_serving --backend sglang-oai  --dataset-name random --random-input-len 512 --random-output-len 1024 --random-range-ratio 1 --num-prompts 20 --max-concurrency 1 --output-file res.jsonl --port 30001 --warmup-requests 10\r\ncurl http://127.0.0.1:30001/flush_cache\r\npython3 -m sglang.bench_serving --backend sglang-oai  --dataset-name random --random-input-len 512 --random-output-len 1024 --random-range-ratio 1 --num-prompts 200 --max-concurrency 32 --output-file res.jsonl --port 30001 --warmup-requests 10\r\n\r\n\r\n+----+-------------------+--------------------+---------------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+----------------+------------------+---------------+-----------------------+\r\n|    |   max_concurrency |   input_throughput |   output_throughput |   mean_ttft_ms |   median_ttft_ms |   p99_ttft_ms |   mean_tpot_ms |   median_tpot_ms |   p99_tpot_ms |   per_user_throughput |\r\n+====+===================+====================+=====================+================+==================+===============+================+==================+===============+=======================+\r\n|  0 |             1.000 |            185.327 |             370.654 |         33.437 |           32.540 |        40.164 |          2.667 |            2.667 |         2.675 |               370.6